            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#洪水后过敏体质要特别注意#】医生提醒，暴雨洪水过后，过敏体质的人要特别注意，若食用了发霉变质的食物，可能出现霉菌感染；吸入一定量霉菌孢子或菌丝...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B4%AA%E6%B0%B4%E5%90%8E%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E4%BD%93%E8%B4%A8%E8%A6%81%E7%89%B9%E5%88%AB%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B4%AA%E6%B0%B4%E5%90%8E%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E4%BD%93%E8%B4%A8%E8%A6%81%E7%89%B9%E5%88%AB%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#洪水后过敏体质要特别注意#</span></a>】医生提醒，暴雨洪水过后，过敏体质的人要特别注意，若食用了发霉变质的食物，可能出现霉菌感染；吸入一定量霉菌孢子或菌丝，可能诱发霉菌过敏性哮喘。对于被洪水浸泡的家具等，要尽快烘干并使用具有除霉菌功效的清洁剂。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>   <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4932497721720862" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hgpfr051ehj61vg11ykjl02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/mn5U3ZxNlx087E71Ke5a01041200fAQ60E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691701938&amp;ssig=gfRCsySgDn&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/1DKK8gRalx087E70rq6k010412008bgZ0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691701938&amp;ssig=2EDPt5jRRL&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/dei6ouP2lx087E70uqw0010412005fmN0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691701938&amp;ssig=HUbRRKw5m7&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4932497721720862&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
